SCHEMA: governance/topology_edge.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.governance.topology_edge
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Canonical edge record for topology graph artifacts.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record topology_edge
  required:
    - edge_id: id
    - from_node_id: id
    - to_node_id: id
    - edge_kind: enum(depends_on|produces|consumes|validates|enforces|migrates)
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- Edge identifiers and ordering must be deterministic.
